snippet.title: A Vampyre Story: Year One - Adventure Game KickStarter Pledge Drive Animation
snippet.description:
http://www.kickstarter.com/projects/876324751/a-vampyre-story-year-one?ref=live
Award winning graphic Adventure A Vampyre Story gets a episodic prequel through Kickstarter.
This is an animated CG video that we made at Autumn Moon Entertainment for our Kickstarter campaign to raise money for our Graphic Adventure A Vampyre Story: Year One. If you like the video please head over to Kickstarter and pledge.
http://www.kickstarter.com/projects/876324751/a-vampyre-story-year-one?ref=live
